  "prompt": "I am going to organising an party, for that I need to clean my home on or before 31/12/2017. So suggest me cleaning service company in Perth?",
  "response": "For your end-of-year party, you'll want to ensure your home is sparkling clean. Here are some reputable cleaning service companies in Perth that you can consider for your needs:\n\n1. **V.I.P. Home Services**:\n   - They offer a wide range of cleaning services, including end-of-lease, carpet, and regular home cleaning. You can book their services online or by calling them directly.\n\n2. **Jim's Cleaning**:\n   - Known for their reliable service, Jim's Cleaning offers various cleaning options, including home cleaning. They have a good reputation and might be able to accommodate your deadline.\n\n3. **Hassle Free Cleaning Services**:\n   - This company specializes in domestic cleaning and might be a good fit for preparing your home for a party. They are known for their professional and thorough service.\n\n4. **Clean Choice Cleaning Services**:\n   - Offering both residential and commercial cleaning, Clean Choice could be a great choice for a thorough clean before your event. They have positive reviews and competitive pricing.\n\n5. **Maid2Match**:\n   - Maid2Match provides personalized cleaning services with a focus on customer satisfaction. They might offer packages that could fit your needs for the party.\n\nWhen contacting these companies, make sure to mention your specific deadline of December 31, 2017, to ensure they can accommodate your schedule. It's also a good idea to ask for a quote and any possible discounts for first-time customers or for booking during the holiday season.\n\nGood luck with your party preparations!",
